    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir tkDeenas nahze pee\nDahwidu winnam par Paligu/\nteekins tas Lehgeris tik leels tap-\npe/ ka weens Deewa Lehgeris.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ſchee irr to Wirfneeku\nPulki/ kas us Raxru apbrunnno-\njahs/ un pee Dahwidu uhs Ee-\nbronn nahze/ ka tee Saula Keh-\nnixa Walstu winnam peegreestu/\npehz ta KUNGA Wahrdu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "To Behrnu Juhda/ kas\npreekſchturramas Bruknas un\nSchkehpus neffe/bija feſch tuhſ-\nſtochi un aſtonſints us Raxru\ngattawi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "No Sihmeana Behrneeni\nbija / ſeptin tuhkſtoſchi un ſints\nſipri warreni Raxra-Wihri.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "No Lewja Behrneem /\ntſchetri tuhkſtochi un feſchſints.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Jojadus bija to Aä-\nroniteru Waldneeks / un ar to\ntrihs tuhkſtochi un ſeptinsints.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Zadaks weens ſiprs\nwarrens Puifis / un no winna\nTehwa Namma bija diwideſmits\ndiwi Leeli-Kungi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un no Benjaminna Behr-\nneem bija Saula Brahtu trihs\ntuhkſtoſchi/ jo lihds tam Laſkain\nbija Daudi / kas wehl pee Saula\nNamna turrejahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un no Eewaima Behr-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "neem dtwideſmits tuhkſtoſchi\naſtonſints ſipri warreni Wil-\nkam leela Slawa bija fa-\nTehwu Namma.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un no Manaffus pr\nZilts aſtonpadefinits tuhkſtoſ-\nkas pee Wahrdceim faukti ktu-\nka tee nahktu Dahwidu par Ka\nnimu eezelt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un no Ibsaschara Be-\nneem/ kas Laikus gudri faſr-\nte / kas Israekim bij jadar-\nto paſchu Wirfneeku bija dt-\nſints/ un wiſſi winnu Bra-\ndarrija pehz winnu Wahrida.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "No Sebulana/ kas Ka\nra iſgahje ar wiſtadahm Ka-\nBruknahm apbrunnnoti / b-\npeeſdefinits tuhkſtoſchi/ ar dr-\nſchu Sirpi ſawā Kahrtā ee-\nRaufchanas ſtahwedami.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un no Nawtalus b-\ntuhkſtoſchi Leeli-Kungi / un-\nteem trihsdeſmits ſeptin tuhk-\nſchi/ kas preekſchturramas Bru-\nnas un Schkehpus walkaja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un no teem Daniteeer-\nkas us Raxru gattawi bija /\nwideſmits un aſton tuhkſto-\nun feſchſints.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un no Absera/ kas Ka-\nra iſgahje us Raufchanu gat-\nwi/bija tſchetrideſmits tuhkſto-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 37,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un no teem pahr Jar-\nneefcheem / no teem Rubben-\nreem / un Gaditeeem un pi-\nZilti Manaffus/ ar wiſtada-\nRaxru-Bruknahm/ ſints un-\nwideſmits tuhkſtocht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 38,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiſſi ſchee Raxra-Wih-\n"
    }
  ],
